  "summary": "This proposal outlines interfaces for wrapping [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) or ETH to [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) and unwrap ERC-721 to ERC-20 or ETH. A function oracle feeds mint/burn prices based on an embedded equation of Function Oracle Automated Market Maker(FOAMM), which executes and clears the mint and burn of NFT.",
